{"tid":2200009,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雪碧砸400萬整型「動15次大手術」　整片頭皮掀開…友看照片嚇到狂搖頭","createTime":"2020-09-12T15:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T16:43:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"81a196b9a72c973bd3545749db026c612a3c5bf2","tid":2200009,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"網紅雪碧擁有亮麗的外貌，曾在節目上大方自曝整型，不過最近拍攝YouTube影片，坦承以前其實仍有所保留，實際動過刀的部位比大家知道的更多。她大爆自己的整型辛酸史，為了變漂亮花費將近400萬元、動過約15次的大手術，最痛的一次是把頭皮掀開裝矽膠，現在頭上還留有3根骨釘。<br />\n<br />\n雪碧跟好友雲嫣一起拍片，揭露當年步上整型這條路的原因：「我覺得我的化妝技術沒辦法讓我更有自信心了。」為了提升到更好的狀態，所以決定用整型的方式改善。她動過眼睛、臥蠶、鼻子，也曾抽脂補胸部和屁股，加上每隔一段時間就要打玻尿酸、少女針、肉毒來保養，至今約花了400萬元在整型和微整上。<br />\n<br />\n雪碧坦言，這10年以來大約動過15次大手術，其中最痛的一次就是墊額頭，因為要在額頭放進矽膠墊片，必須把頭皮整片掀開，放完墊片之後再縫回去，現在頭上有3根骨釘，而且切割的部位一直長不太出頭髮。她還受到慘痛的教訓，因為做完手術後輕忽，不到1個月就去按摩，結果趴著的姿勢導致墊片移位，只好再去做一次手術調整回來。<br />\n<br />\n雪碧秀出自己的頭部X光照，問雲嫣「這樣妳敢去做額頭嗎」，嚇得對方連連搖頭拒絕。藉由這支影片，她想提醒大家，整型必須承受修復期的不適，所以動手術之前一定要做好心理準備，也要記得多諮詢、多看別人案例、謹慎評估選哪間醫院，更重要的是不要盲目追求流行，以自己的五官條件整出最適合的模樣。"},{"pid":"6e07a5027aea7ad0d53ee9bb605418cd02d7338f","tid":2200009,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5136/d5136278.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5136%2Fd5136278.jpg&h=9cf5b923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲雪碧用整型方式讓自己變得更美、更有自信。（圖／翻攝自雪碧Instagram）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5136/d5136274.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5136%2Fd5136274.jpg&h=cb5aac6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5136/d5136276.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5136%2Fd5136276.jpg&h=897fab11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲雪碧公開墊額頭手術前後照片。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／SS真雪碧無雙）"},{"pid":"2bde937f60618eb79d044be5a9f855e71fdb53bf","tid":2200009,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5136/d5136277.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5136%2Fd5136277.jpg&h=45d5ab8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲雪碧提醒大家，想整型一定要能承受修復期。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／SS真雪碧無雙）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=04IN6hfHBXY&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D04IN6hfHBXY%26feature%3Demb_title&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513XPcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=d15c4c1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=04IN6hfHBXY&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"bf1482eda54bb0024a31724418693b4ecbb03f01","tid":2200009,"uid":271334,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T15:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個蛇精女 膠到咁都女神<br />\n明明就整容失敗+ 上癮"},{"pid":"677f9fe62b35823df6b539ce37ae66fc4aeb5b13","tid":2200009,"uid":131188,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T15:48:32.000Z","msg":"仲以為係呢個換新包裝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/uJ0cMlNh70DUI2etc0Ss0O9TE8Ok9DViawtdbKcPLFD4HedLAW0uzBAxnTDUHo2NLEnfr66ZvpNBedLDcpy3uDBHIrXjsRLQ4Rd12Kon3c_4yrUxWNroa1Yz6_0nDz_IXAQFeVleR2A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FuJ0cMlNh70DUI2etc0Ss0O9TE8Ok9DViawtdbKcPLFD4HedLAW0uzBAxnTDUHo2NLEnfr66ZvpNBedLDcpy3uDBHIrXjsRLQ4Rd12Kon3c_4yrUxWNroa1Yz6_0nDz_IXAQFeVleR2A&h=73083622&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e669260851309671d786b5505bf13d8bf42d54b","tid":2200009,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T16:35:40.000Z","msg":"人工得滯無興趣"},{"pid":"c296b9a14b3e27da8082e15cb19